{"content": "I need to multiply 926 \u00d7 277 in base 11.\n\n**Step 1: Convert 926 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 926\u2081\u2081 = 9\u00d711\u00b2 + 2\u00d711\u00b9 + 6\u00d711\u2070\n- = 9\u00d7121 + 2\u00d711 + 6\u00d71\n- = 1089 + 22 + 6\n- = 1117\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Convert 277 (base 11) to base 10**\n- 277\u2081\u2081 = 2\u00d711\u00b2 + 7\u00d711\u00b9 + 7\u00d711\u2070\n- = 2\u00d7121 + 7\u00d711 + 7\u00d71\n- = 242 + 77 + 7\n- = 326\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Multiply in base 10**\n- 1117 \u00d7 326 = 364,142\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 4: Convert 364,142 (base 10) to base 11**\n- 364142 \u00f7 11 = 33103 R 9\n- 33103 \u00f7 11 = 3009 R 4\n- 3009 \u00f7 11 = 273 R 6\n- 273 \u00f7 11 = 24 R 9\n- 24 \u00f7 11 = 2 R 2\n- 2 \u00f7 11 = 0 R 2\n\nReading remainders from bottom to top: 229649\n\n**Answer: 229649**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 363, "completion_tokens": 398}